{"version":3,"term":{"cols":80,"rows":24},"timestamp":1783442100,"command":"bash /tmp/claude-1000/-home-rfiszel-windmill--worktrees-ruben-win-2138-clarify-cli-auto-targets-correct-workspace-in-fork-branches/8d89d02f-45ab-4604-9316-ff8905f80ecc/scratchpad/demo.sh","env":{"SHELL":"/usr/bin/zsh"}}
[0.002, "o", "\u001b[1;35m$ wmill workspace fork myfork myfork --yes\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.157, "o", "\u001b[0m\u001b[31m\u001b[34mUsing workspace 'main' (matched current git branch 'main') вҶ’ demo on http://localhost:8340/ (profile 'demo')\u001b[39m\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[34mYou are forking workspace (demo)\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b[34m\u001b[34mCreating forked workspace: myfork...\u001b[39m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[0.021, "o", "\u001b[34m\u001b[32mвң… Created forked workspace wm-fork-myfork\u001b[39m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[34mCreated forked workspace wm-fork-myfork. To start contributing to your fork, create and push edits to the branch `wm-fork/main/myfork` by using the command:\r\n\r\n\t\u001b[37mgit checkout -b wm-fork/main/myfork\u001b[39m\r\n\r\nWhile on the branch `wm-fork/main/myfork`, every wmill command (sync pull/push, script run, ...) automatically targets the fork workspace `wm-fork-myfork` вҖ” no --workspace flag or profile switch needed. The remote comes from the base branch `main`'s entry in wmill.yaml's workspaces section, and auth is reused from that workspace's saved profile.\r\n\r\nTo merge changes back to the parent workspace, you can:\r\n  - Use the CLI: \u001b[37mgit checkout wm-fork/main/myfork && wmill workspace merge\u001b[39m\r\n  - Use the Merge UI from the forked workspace home page\r\n  - Use git: \u001b[37mgit checkout main && git merge wm-fork/main/myfork && wmill sync push\u001b[39m\r\n  See: https://www.windmill.dev/docs/advanced/workspace_forks\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[0.005, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;35m$ git checkout -b wm-fork/main/myfork\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "Switched to a new branch 'wm-fork/main/myfork'\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;35m$ wmill workspace\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.113, "o", "в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\r\nв”Ӯ  name  в”Ӯ  remote                  в”Ӯ  workspace id  в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ  \u001b[4mdemo\u001b[24m  в”Ӯ  \u001b[4mhttp://localhost:8340/\u001b[24m  в”Ӯ  \u001b[4mdemo\u001b[24m          в”Ӯ\r\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[34mActive: \u001b[1m\u001b[32mdemo\u001b[39m\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[0.002, "o", "\u001b[34m\u001b[33mNote: you are on fork branch `wm-fork/main/myfork` вҖ” wmill commands automatically target the fork workspace `wm-fork-myfork` here, regardless of the active profile. Use --workspace to override.\u001b[39m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[0.004, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;35m$ wmill sync pull --dry-run\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.129, "o", "\u001b[0m\u001b[31m\u001b[34m\u001b[32mAutomatically targeting fork workspace `wm-fork-myfork` (fork of `demo` on http://localhost:8340/, profile 'demo'), resolved from git branch `wm-fork/main/myfork`. Use --workspace to override.\u001b[39m\u001b[39m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.013, "o", "\u001b[34m\u001b[90mComputing the files to update locally to match remote (taking wmill.yaml into account)\u001b[39m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
